<p>I take lot of notes about the books I read and I find myself often in a place where I'd like to share a particular passage from a book, hence this section.</p>

<p>Happy reading about reading :)</p>

<div class="books-grid">
    {% for item in collections.reading %}
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">
            <article class="book-card">
                <div class="book-card-cover">
                    <img
                        src="/assets/reading/{{ item.fileSlug }}.jpg"
                        alt="Cover of {{ item.data.title }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
                <footer class="book-card-info">
                    <h3>{{ item.data.title }}</h3>
                    {% if item.data.author %}
                        <p class="book-card-author">{{ item.data.author }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                </footer>
            </article>
        </a>
    {% endfor %}
</div>
